### Credentials — never commit (this repo is PUBLIC) ###
# An OpenSSH private key and the JetBrains Marketplace publish token were previously
# tracked here. These rules are written AFTER the fact, so they do not retroactively
# protect anything already in history — the history purge is tracked separately.
# NOTE the leading slash: these are repo-ROOT key files. An unanchored `astagfirullah`
# also matches the source package dir src/main/kotlin/com/alfayedoficial/astagfirullah,
# which would silently make every new file in that package un-addable.
/astagfirullah
/astagfirullah.pub
*.pem
*.p12
*.jks
*.keystore
id_rsa
id_ed25519
*.key
secrets.properties
local.properties
# Publish/sign credentials are supplied via environment variables
# (see `publishPlugin`/`signPlugin` in build.gradle.kts), never via a tracked file.
**/gradle.properties.local